</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uwynnie0rodcetnife.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Wynnie 0 Rodcet Nife</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/29/01 5:01:25 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Well....</span><hr size=1> I dunno.. I see it a bit differently...<br>
<br>
Evils will have strongholds on certain areas, this is obvious.  Newts and Goods will have a harder time establishing said strongholds.<br>
<br>
Neutrals will be a very strong force, and most likely the primary force against evils, coming very close in numbers.  Goods will, unfortunately, be scrapping most of SZ's life. <br>
<br>
Evil will not bend to either newts nor goods, to further their own gains.  However, they will find that outside of their sphere of ownership (2-4 zone spread from cities), they will meet heavy resistance from the two other teams (call it carry-over from Team PvP, although newts and goods probably won't consciously be working together, they will save personal grudges for after elimation of evil parties).  Newts and goods, however, will be slightly more likely to at least acknowledge possible sharing of areas, if for no other reason than to counter the straight monopolization of evil ownership.<br>
<br>
Again, it's all just babble speak right now.  Who knows what will happen.. let's just say that underutilized zones might see some more action now, as people try and find a way to gain abilities under the radar.<br>
<br>
Just my 2c <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uiamwotan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>I am Wotan</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.thegamevine.com/~Wotan_Rogue/yinyang.gif border=0 BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/29/01 5:39:57 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.thegamevine.com/~Wotan_Rogue/mask2a.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Well....</span><hr size=1> Evil will dominate, Goodies and neuters will have an uneasy alliance, and players with sack will go where they want.<br>
